trans-unit.source: An XML element that contains a unique network address that a client uses to communicate with a service endpoint.
trans-unit.target: XML 項目，包含用戶端用來與服務端點通訊的唯一網路位址。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.EndpointAddressElementBase" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.EndpointAddressElementBase" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the URI for the endpoint.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定端點的 URI。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Uri" /> that identifies the network location for the endpoint.
trans-unit.target: 識別端點之網路位置的 <see cref="T:System.Uri" />。

trans-unit.source: The configuration element to be copied over.
Copies the content of a specified configuration element to this configuration element.
trans-unit.target: 將指定之組態項目的內容複製到這個組態項目。
<paramref name="source" /> 為 <see langword="null" /> 或是空的。

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of address headers for the endpoints that the builder can create.
trans-unit.target: 取得產生器 (Builder) 可建立之端點位址標頭的集合。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.AddressHeaderCollectionElement" /> that contains address information for the endpoint.
trans-unit.target: 包含端點之位址資訊的 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.AddressHeaderCollectionElement" />。

trans-unit.source: Gets the identity for the endpoint.
An <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.IdentityElement" /> that provides an identity that enables the authentication of an endpoint by other endpoints exchanging messages with it.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.IdentityElement" /> 所提供的識別，可讓其他端點與此端點交換訊息時啟用端點驗證。

trans-unit.source: Initializes this endpoint address with the content of the specified endpoint address.
trans-unit.target: 使用指定之端點位址的內容，初始化這個端點位址。
<paramref name="endpointAddress" /> 為 <see langword="null" /> 或是空的。

trans-unit.source: Gets a <see cref="T:System.Configuration.ConfigurationPropertyCollection" /> instance that contains a collection of <see cref="T:System.Configuration.ConfigurationProperty" /> objects that can be attributes or <see cref="T:System.Configuration.ConfigurationElement" /> objects of this configuration element.
trans-unit.target: 取得 <see cref="T:System.Configuration.ConfigurationPropertyCollection" /> 執行個體，其中包含可能是屬性之 <see cref="T:System.Configuration.ConfigurationProperty" /> 物件的集合或這個組態項目之 <see cref="T:System.Configuration.ConfigurationElement" /> 物件的集合。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Configuration.ConfigurationPropertyCollection" /> instance that contains a collection of <see cref="T:System.Configuration.ConfigurationProperty" /> objects that can be attributes or <see cref="T:System.Configuration.ConfigurationElement" /> objects of this configuration element.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Configuration.ConfigurationPropertyCollection" /> 執行個體，其中包含可能是屬性之 <see cref="T:System.Configuration.ConfigurationProperty" /> 物件或這個組態項目之 <see cref="T:System.Configuration.ConfigurationElement" /> 物件的集合。
